[0.000, "o", "# Step 13: Ask Build Agent for Implementation Guidance\r\n"]
[2.028, "o", "\r\n$ copado-hx ai ask --agent build \"What Apex metadata should I create for a lead scoring feature?\"\r\n"]
[46.301, "o", "\u001b[32mв•­в”Ђ\u001b[0m\u001b[32m [Agent] Build Agent вЂ” Apex generation, metadata analysis, troubleshooting \u001b[0m\u001b[32mв”Ђ\u001b[0m\u001b[32mв”Ђв•®\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m I'll search for best practices and check your org for relevant existing      \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m metadata at the same time!                                                   \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m Now let me also check for any existing Lead-related custom fields and        \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m objects in your org:                                                         \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m Great вЂ” I can see there are **no existing lead scoring custom fields or Apex \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m classes** in your org yet. Here's a comprehensive recommendation for the     \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m Apex metadata you should create for a lead scor"]
[0.000, "o", "ing feature:                  \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ---                                                                          \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ## рџЋЇ Lead Scoring Feature вЂ” Recommended Apex Metadata                       \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ### 1. рџ“¦ Custom Fields on `Lead`                                            \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m Before writing Apex, you'll need a few fields on the `Lead` object:          \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m | Field Label | API Name "]
[0.000, "o", "| Type | Purpose |                                  \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m |---|---|---|---|                                                            \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m | Lead Score | `Lead_Score__c` | Number | Computed score (0вЂ“100) |           \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m | Score Last Updated | `Score_Last_Updated__c` | DateTime | Audit timestamp  \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m |                                                                            \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m | Scoring Notes | `Scoring_Notes__c` | Text Area | Breakdown of score        \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m factors |                                                                    \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ---                                                                          \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ### 2. "]
[0.000, "o", "рџ§  Apex Class вЂ” Scoring Engine (`LeadScoringService`)                 \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m The **core business logic** class. Responsible for calculating scores based  \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m on configurable criteria (industry, company size, lead source, email domain, \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m etc.).                                                                       \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ```xml                                                                       \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m LeadScoringService.cls                                                       \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ```                                                                          \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m **Responsibilities:**                                                        \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m - Accept a `List<Lead>` and return a `Map<Id, Integer>` of scores            \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m - Apply scoring rules (e.g., +20 for `Industry = Technology`, +15 for        \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m `LeadSource = Web`, +10 for company size > 500)                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m - Stateless and bulkified (no SOQL/DML inside loops)                         \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ---                                                                          \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ### 3. вљЎ Apex Trigger вЂ” `LeadScoringTrigger`                                \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                         "]
[0.000, "o", "     \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m Fires on `Lead` **insert** and **update** to invoke the scoring service.     \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ```xml                                                                       \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m LeadScoringTrigger.trigger                                                   \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ```                                                                          \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m **Best practice:** Keep the trigger thin вЂ” delegate all logic to the         \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m handler.                                                                     \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ---                                                   "]
[0.000, "o", "                       \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ### 4. рџЋ›пёЏ Apex Class вЂ” Trigger Handler (`LeadScoringTriggerHandler`)         \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m Separates trigger logic from business logic, following the **Single          \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m Responsibility Principle**.                                                  \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ```xml                                                                       \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m LeadScoringTriggerHandler.cls                                                \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ```                                                                          \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                "]
[0.000, "o", "                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m **Responsibilities:**                                                        \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m - Handle `before insert` / `before update` contexts                          \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m - Call `LeadScoringService` and apply scores to `Trigger.new`                \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ---                                                                          \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ### 5. рџ”„ Apex Class вЂ” Batch/Queueable (`LeadScoringBatchJob`)               \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m For **retroactive scoring** of existing leads at scale.                      \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m            "]
[0.000, "o", "                                                                  \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ```xml                                                                       \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m LeadScoringBatchJob.cls  (implements Database.Batchable<SObject>)            \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m ```                                                                          \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m **Responsibilities:**                                                        \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m - Query all unscored or stale leads                                          \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m - Invoke `LeadScoringService` per batch chunk                                \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m - Update `Lead_Score__c` and `Score_Last_Updated__c`                         \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mв”‚"]
